Invocation Name: q. time daily prayers
des: These Vedic prayers are in Sanskrit and are designed for each day of the week in terms of praising God, seek blessings from god and practice the development of a mindset to start the day and the meditational healing that could help to deal with the challenges of the day from a mindset that is prepared for the unexpected or chaotic scenarios that any day could bring.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
